data.description: Towne Park Village is a popular place to call home! You'll love living in this 2 story lapis home design with 5 BR, 3 BA and 2 car garage. The open kitchen/dining/living area is great for entertaining. The down 5th bedroom option with full bath is a great space for guests or as a bonus room. Upstairs is the owner's suite with walk-in closet and slope ceilings for a grand feel. The attached owner's spa bath had large walk-in shower and plenty of storage space. The spacious 3 upstairs bedrooms share a secondary bath. Enjoy the outdoors under the optional covered patio. Let your children run around the community playground, take your pooch for a run at the dog park or enjoy the quite under the gazebo. Offered by: K. Hovnanian of Houston III, L.L.C.
